cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.SI, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a deep neural network model for predicting the popularity of online videos, which involves a wide range of features and multiple competitors. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Among these, cs.LG is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing a deep learning model. The other categories are also relevant as the paper deals with multimedia content, social networks, and language processing.
